<br>
&quot;Maybe your right, but an old coot I am not.&quot;<br>
<br>
Poseidon looks at Madmartigan and leaves him alone. <br>
<br>
&quot;Sorry about that, go about your ways. Apparently Artemis knows full well what is best in my jurisdiction.&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 360<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/10/02 10:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~sigh~</span><hr size=1> ~She looked to her uncle as he transformed into his human shape and shook her head.~<br>
&quot; I do hate when anyone puts words in my mouth. I dont care who does it, let it be you, or Zeus...I DI NOT say I knew what was best. But murdering someone just because he is trying to survive, that is petty dear uncle. It would be something else if he stole money or jewels, but a loaf of bread...Come now.....&quot;<br>
~She shook her head and vanished in a burst of silver lights.~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 303<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/11/02 1:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.uvic.ca/grs/bowman/myth/images/haifa/h89.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~sigh~</span><hr size=1> The god screamed out to Artemis as she vanished.<br>
<br>
&quot;But you interceded Artemis, your part was thus played so you did stop me from carrying out retribution in mine own way though you did make me see that I could be less harsh.&quot;<br>
<br>
The sky crackle with lightning and a hail storm poured down from the greyish clouds. Another flash came and Poseidon flew away in the guise of a bird. <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 199<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/11/02 3:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~sigh~</span><hr size=1> &quot;Yes, yes i'm fine.&quot; Said madmartigan when Artemis questioned him. Madmartigan stood watching as the two immortals spoke. A creek of a smile formed on Mad's lips a he realized he had won this small battle, with the help of Artemis of cource. As Posiden started to leave, Madmartigan stuck his toung out at him and dissappeared into the croud, and out of the city, hoping to make his way home... to food he wouldn't be punished for eating. &quot;Thank you Artemis,&quot; He shouted to the sky, as he ran, hoping she would somehow hear him. &quot;I owe you one!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=253.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=253.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </